---

<div id="contact" class="relative bg-secondary py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden scroll-mt-24">
    <!-- Background Curve/Wave SVG -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full transform -translate-y-1/2">
        <svg
            viewBox="0 0 1200 120"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            class="w-full h-24 fill-white"
        >
            <path
                d="M321.39,56.44c58-10.79,114.16-30.13,172-41.86,82.39-16.72,168.19-17.73,250.45-.39C823.78,31,906.67,72,985.66,92.83c70.05,18.48,146.53,26.09,214.34,3V0H0V27.35A600.21,600.21,0,0,0,321.39,56.44Z"
                class="shape-fill"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <div
        class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"
    >
        <!-- Left Column: Text & CTA -->
        <div class="text-center lg:text-left text-white">
            <span
                class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 text-white rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 border border-white/40 shadow-sm"
            >
                Hablemos
            </span>
            <h2
                class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight"
            >
                ¿Listo para tu <span
                    class="text-accent underline decoration-primary decoration-4 underline-offset-8"
                    >Próxima Aventura?</span
                >
            </h2>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                Diseñamos y planificamos el viaje perfecto a la costa peruana.
                Déjanos tus datos y nos pondremos en contacto contigo en menos
                de 24 horas.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
                    >
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded"
                            >phone_in_talk</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span
                            class="block text-accent text-xs uppercase font-bold"
                            >WhatsApp</span
                        >
                        <span class="font-bold text-lg">+34 653 252 923</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
                    >
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded">mail</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span
                            class="block text-accent text-xs uppercase font-bold"
                            >Email</span
                        >
                        <span class="font-bold text-lg"
                            >info@spotstosurfperu.com</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
                    >
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded">location_on</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span
                            class="block text-accent text-xs uppercase font-bold"
                            >Ubicación</span
                        >
                        <span class="font-bold text-lg"
                            >Miraflores, Lima - Perú</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Form Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl relative">
            <div
                class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-20 h-20 bg-orange-400 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-50"
            >
            </div>

            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Envíanos un mensaje
            </h3>

            <form class="space-y-4">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div>
                        <label
                            for="name"
                            class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-1"
                            >Nombre</label
                        >
                        <input
                            id="name"
                            type="text"
                            placeholder="Tu nombre"
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm font-medium"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label
                            for="email"
                            class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-1"
                            >Email</label
                        >
                        <input
                            id="email"
                            type="email"
                            placeholder="tu@email.com"
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm font-medium"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label
                        for="interest"
                        class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-1"
                        >Interés Principal</label
                    >
                    <div class="relative">
                        <select
                            id="interest"
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 appearance-none focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"
                        >
                            <option>Trip a Medida (Custom)</option>
                            <option>Paquete Surf (Fixed)</option>
                            <option>Clases de Surf</option>
                            <option>Alojamiento</option>
                            <option>Tour gastronómico</option>
                            <option>Otro</option>
                        </select>
                        <div
                            class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="material-symbols-rounded text-gray-400 text-sm"
                                >expand_more</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label
                            for="message"
                            class="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 uppercase mb-1"
                            >Mensaje</label
                        >
                        <textarea
                            id="message"
                            rows="4"
                            placeholder="Cuéntanos más sobre tu viaje ideal..."
                            class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm font-medium resize-none"
                        ></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-orange-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                    >
                        Enviar Mensaje
                        <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-sm"
                            >send</span
                        >
                    </button>
                </div>

                <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-600 mt-4">
                    Al enviar aceptas nuestros <a
                        href="/privacy"
                        class="text-secondary underline font-bold"
                        >Términos y Privacidad</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
